{"text_id":246306,"tokens":["When"," it"," comes"," to"," staying"," after"," school"," for"," activities"," it"," can"," be"," difficult"," to"," decide"," if"," students"," should"," be"," rewarded"," or"," if"," it"," should"," be"," mandatory","."," Both"," approaches"," have"," pros"," and"," cons"," that"," need"," to"," be"," weighed"," and"," considered"," when"," making"," this"," decision","."," Additionally",","," the"," impact"," on"," students","\u2019"," academic"," performance"," and"," overall"," well","-","being"," should"," also"," be"," taken"," into"," account","."," ","\n","Reward","ing"," students"," for"," staying"," after"," school"," for"," activities"," can"," be"," an"," effective"," way"," to"," incentiv","ize"," them"," to"," participate","."," Rewards"," can"," take"," the"," form"," of"," financial"," incentives",","," such"," as"," scholarships"," or"," stip","ends",","," or"," non","-","financial"," incentives",","," such"," as"," extra"," credit"," or"," recognition","."," One"," pro"," of"," rewarding"," students"," is"," that"," it"," can"," motivate"," them"," to"," strive"," for"," excellence"," and"," become"," more"," invested"," in"," staying"," after"," school"," for"," activities","."," Another"," pro"," is"," that"," it"," can"," act"," as"," a"," reward"," for"," good"," academic"," performance"," since"," many"," of"," the"," activities"," that"," students"," stay"," after"," for"," are"," related"," to"," their"," academic"," work","."," ","\n","However",","," there"," are"," also"," some"," potential"," downsides"," to"," rewarding"," students","."," For"," example",","," students"," may"," be"," more"," inclined"," to"," prioritize"," the"," rewards"," over"," the"," activity"," itself",","," making"," it"," more"," a"," drawn","-","out"," chore"," than"," an"," enjoyable"," passion","."," Additionally",","," teachers"," may"," be"," less"," likely"," to"," challenge"," students"," if"," they"," believe"," students","